  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A minimal typing test that treats your speed as \"a quiet line of text\" — measuring WPM and accuracy and rendering an animated history of your runs over time, rather than the usual loud gamified dashboard.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Typing speed as a quiet line of text\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/typing-test-animated-history/landing.png\" alt=\"Typing speed as a quiet line of text\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/typing-test-animated-history/landing.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/typing-test-animated-history/landing.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/typing-test-animated-history/landing.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/typing-test-animated-history/landing.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Typing speed as a quiet line of text\" width=\"1440\" height=\"813\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1440×813\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Typing speed as a quiet line of text</figcaption>\n</figure>",
